      <title>图斯克表示无需会见泽伦斯基即可平息边境抗议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/tusk-says-no-need-to-meet-zelenskiy-to-defuse-border-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总理唐纳德·图斯克表示，没有必要在边境与乌克兰总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基会面，以解除农民的封锁，该封锁导致来自饱受战争蹂躏的国家的货运中断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/tusk-says-no-need-to-meet-zelenskiy-to-defuse-border-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 11:17:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
